{"success": true, "message": "Fetched question.", "data": {"showTimer": true, "showAttemptInsight": true, "playSounds": true, "dontShowCorrectAnswerImmediately": false, "_id": "64c0e7ab6f5bfc7ab78ae6d9", "classes": [], "exams": ["615d7713c52ffa3c944600e3"], "subjects": ["615d708dbd4a37c4058ee5a8"], "chapters": ["615d6fec2b295b085ab6eb8f"], "topics": [], "concepts": [], "previousYearPapers": [{"_id": "61a8bf0fc821b6514e527d77", "title": "BITSAT 2013", "isVisible": true}], "position": 0, "type": "singleCorrect", "level": 3, "approximateTimeRequired": 120, "question": {"text": "A light inextensible string that goes over a smooth fixed pulley as shown in the figure connects two blocks of masses $0.36 \\mathrm{~kg}$ and $0.72 \\mathrm{~kg}$. Taking $\\mathrm{g}=10 \\mathrm{~m} / \\mathrm{s}^{2},$ find the work done $(\\mathrm{in}$\r\n\r\njoules) by the string on the block of mass $0.36 \\mathrm{~kg}$ during the first second after the system is released from rest.\r\n\r\n<img src=\"https://cdn-question-pool.getmarks.app/pyq/bitsat/i7gKSnXmc1MN1Q3bNmoSV1vXdMYrIOUkiYHPtD9sntw.original.fullsize.png\">", "image": null}, "options": [{"id": "dFAQH", "text": "$4 \\mathrm{~J}$", "isCorrect": false, "image": null}, {"id": "6nCtb", "text": "$2 \\mathrm{~J}$", "isCorrect": false, "image": null}, {"id": "72Utl", "text": "$8 \\mathrm{~J}$", "isCorrect": true, "image": null}, {"id": "3LiD3", "text": "$10 \\mathrm{~J}$", "isCorrect": false, "image": null}], "correctValue": null, "solution": {"text": "Given $m=0.36 \\mathrm{~kg}, M=0.72 \\mathrm{~kg}$. The figure shows the forces on $m$ and $M$. When the system is released, let the acceleration be $a$. Then\r\n\r\n$T-m g=m a$\r\n\r\n$M g-T=M a$\r\n\r\n$$\r\n\r\na=\\frac{(M-m) g}{M+m}=g / 3\r\n\r\n$$\r\n\r\nand $T=4 \\mathrm{mg} / 3$\r\n\r\nFor block m:\r\n\r\n$$\r\n\r\nu=0, a=g / 3, t=1, s=?\r\n\r\n$$\r\n\r\n<img src=\"https://cdn-question-pool.getmarks.app/pyq/bitsat/_LD6QYhzhQSmiBzK3EKnfY0Rr12eqtvfzy_3HP0QUNg.original.fullsize.png\"><br>\r\n\r\n$$\r\n\r\ns=u t+\\frac{1}{2} a t^{2}=0+\\frac{1}{2} \\times \\frac{g}{3} \\times 1^{2}=g / 6\r\n\r\n$$\r\n\r\nWork done by the string on $m$ is\r\n\r\n$$\r\n\r\n\\bar{T} \\bar{s}=T s=4 \\frac{m g}{3} \\times \\frac{g}{6}=\\frac{4 \\times 0.36 \\times 10 \\times 10}{3 \\times 6}=8 \\mathrm{~J}\r\n\r\n$$", "image": null}, "videoSolution": null, "numericalUpperLimit": null, "numericalLowerLimit": null, "questionLabels": [], "__v": 0, "masterId": "MOGBSPYQ76868002", "bucket": "", "category": null, "microConcepts": [], "imageBaseUrl": null, "helperText": null, "isRemoved": false, "cpyqbSubjects": ["61bb58181213731910ea0b70", "61c055eae8ce0dc8a5c62d33", "616057750283de43c87e3e1b", "61964fe0a5a5260118868021", "61964f81a5a526011886801d", "629f39e4ac11b26562e0625b", "616057920283de43c87e3e1e", "615f0c729476412f48314dab", "61a8a2c2e8ce0dc8a5c62d2d", "629105adee9e3ae00d63352b", "629f385f263330a77be9fa7d", "616056cd0283de43c87e3e15", "616057190283de43c87e3e18", "62962075e7f8e9ac4daeafd7", "64d50bd73df7f4a7f3017f6f", "66b79b34d4b564dfab4f94cc", "678ea9a09cc79e5f592bdc11", "67fa5fef4468eb1307ceb0ad", "6807d2ad647479b8e8696479"], "cpyqbChapters": ["616023bf95e073867090a211", "616023bd4bf85baf0acdc7af", "616023bb7fac1bbfb6fab777", "61c089b102f2b15919540e82", "61e7bd7ee55d02038d8af062", "616023bef4c3ea68d46811e1", "61964c773e2489c61bc6319b", "616023be85200f5fc181a4a8", "61bb8228236dd37c5857f9d7", "61964c77f70fa6f1f53faae3", "629109f5ef336ef6f085a231", "629f3a9430ead16c09082830", "629f390f02e524873634489e", "64cc99da08d12fed62b18193", "64eb071d3118f713ecfef408", "66d58535a75f05ee8564f53c", "67921d8c1d5b5072da5e9bfd", "67fdff4f378e1624ea7b6a00", "6809202f3a10446a207fdf10"], "cpyqbExams": ["61a8a124e8ce0dc8a5c62d2c"]}, "fetch_status": true}